++ A Final Rumination
The Triliminal Gates are key to the conflict between **She Who Guards From The Sunlight** and --He Who Devoured The Nine--. Their creation spurred the rift between **Our Lady** and --the Tyrant--. --The Tyrant-- believed that death and war between our worlds was inevitable. **Our Lady** believed that peace between our worlds was not only possible, but necessary.

In that mission, we have failed. Peace between our worlds is now impossible. Our mission now turns to the abatement of harm. For this reason, the final goal of our Covenant is the complete severing of ties between our world and the //Otherworld//.

This concludes the account of the Triliminal Gates used by the --Dardic Sorcerers--, their purpose, and the //Otherworld// that exists beyond that gateway.

May **Our Lady’s Red Right Hand** Guard Us All From --The Nameless One’s Wrath--.

THUS CONCLUDES THIS RECORD

